cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.IT 

This paper deals with the deployment of wireless sensor networks, which is a topic related to computer networks and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses algorithms and decision-making processes, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of statistical models and experimentation with real-world data could also place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
